    <Entry>
      <ID>13</ID>
      <DefaultText>Pinching the rings between thumbs and forefingers, you struggle to bring them together. The force repelling them is not magnetism - it's almost as if someone is holding your hands apart with impossible, contemptuous strength. 

Nevertheless, there must be a way to join these rings. You just haven't found it yet. </DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>14</ID>
      <DefaultText>Examine Vareth. 
{SCRIPT: Node 13 displays if player has ITM_RINGA_ShadowRingVareth}</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
